videos.description: Damian Lillard gets fouled and knocks down two clutch free throws with just over one second left on the clock to seal a 125-124 win over the Pelicans.

videos.description: Damian Lillard scores 50 points on just 20 shots to help the Trail Blazers overcome a 17-point deficit and beat the Pelicans.
